Package org.jets3t.service

Class Summary
Constants Constants used by the S3Service and its implementation classes.
Jets3tProperties Utility class to locate jets3t-specific properties files and make them available from a central place.
S3ObjectsChunk Contains an array of S3objects and a the last key name returned by a prior call to the method.
S3Service A service that handles communication with S3, performing all available actions.
 

Exception Summary
S3ServiceException Exception for use by S3Services and related utilities.
